Configuration file: refpub.properties

The configuration file which holds all the properties needed by the application should be copied in a folder
default folder /opt/refpub/conf

Windows users can use C:\opt\refpub\conf

The configuration file final path must be present in the Restful API's web.xml as:

<context-param>     
  	<param-name>refpub-confFile</param-name>     
	<param-value>/opt/refpub/conf/refpub.properties</param-value>     
</context-param>